import React from 'react'

import Routers from '../../router/Routers'
import Header from '../Header/Header'
import Footer from '../Footer/Footer'
import Home from '../../Pages/Home'


const Layout = () => {
  return (
    <>
    <Header/>
    <Home/>
    <Routers/>
    <Footer/>    
    </>
  )
}

export default Layout
